eastman a former hollywood skin care and makeup expert 
for nine years i have rated the nominees on style 
personality character even the way they walk and talk in 
public eastman said a good self and public image is your most 
valuable asset whether youre a waiter banker housewife or 
shooting for best actress 
eastman rated meryl streep at 97 glenn close 95 sally 
kirkland 92 and holly hunter 90 
