theater barn troupe in this western dutch city where the 
production of the 1952 play is scheduled to open thursday producer 
ina otten said friday 
beckett gave no reasons for his disapproval in the telegram ms 
otten said the 82year old playwright could not immediately be 
reached for comment at his french home 
were putting the play on just the way beckett says it should 
be done except were using women ms otten told the associated 
press she maintained the play would go ahead as scheduled despite 
becketts threat 
wating for godot which calls for an allmale cast of four 
is an absurdist classic widely regarded as the central metaphors 
for the philosophy of existentialism 
