sensational grist for tobacco opponents who seized on the 
information as a major aid in future lawsuits 
the evidence included memorandums that spoke of the hurdle 
of the smoking and health issue of the risk that selling a safer 
cigarette would bring more liability lawsuits and of the public 
relations war against health charges 
the trial began feb 1 except for testimony in early march by 
an addiction expert who described mrs cipollones smoking habits 
