health 
then come more excerpts of mrs cipollones testimony and 
experts on consumer behavior marketing cancer and addiction to 
counter evidence by the plaintiffs experts 
both sides agree on a fundamental decision the jury has to make 
did mrs cipollone believe smoking was legitimately dangerous 
and if she didnt was it the industrys fault 
its going to come down to how much personal responsibility 
you put on her and how much you put on the defendants said 
cipollone attorney cynthia a walters 
