chemist frank durkee testified that a packet of powder zaccaro 
sold to manning tested as cocaine 
tetzlaff who rested his case soon after durkees testimony had 
said in his opening statement the defense will not dispute the 
allegation that he sold a regulated drug this is a case of 
improper and overzealous police conduct 
